data.text: @SenatorCantwell @Seahawks There are an estimated 46 million Kurds worldwide—perhaps even more. For lasting peace in the Middle East, Kurds, like other peoples, should have their own state. Arabs, Turks, and Persians have fought wars that claimed millions of lives. It is time for everyone to say: enough.

@SenatorCantwell @Seahawks The people of Iran demand the fall of the Islamic Republic. After 40,000+ deaths, we reject any nuclear deal. This regime can only be changed by foreign military intervention. Its nuclear program is dangerous for the world. We want freedom.

@SenatorCantwell @Seahawks Every day in Iran protesters are executed after sham trials: summary hearings, forced confessions under torture, denied lawyers, and rushed executions with no real appeals. This is ongoing. Please lead action to stop these crimes. The Iranian people need urgent support.
